      <p><a href="ch66s16.html#MonstersG180">Griffons</a> are powerful, majestic creatures with the characteristics of both <a href="ch73s24.html#MonstersAnimals84">lions</a> and <a href="ch73s18.html#MonstersAnimals59">eagles</a>. From nose to tail, an adult <a href="ch66s16.html#MonstersG180">griffon</a> can measure as much as 8 feet. Neither males nor females are endowed with a mane. A pair of broad, golden wings emerge from the creature's back and span 25 feet or more. A <a href="ch66s16.html#MonstersG180">griffon</a> weighs about 500 pounds.<a href="img/MonstersG.Griffon.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/MonstersG.Griffon.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
      <p>A <a href="ch66s16.html#MonstersG180">griffon</a> cannot speak, but understands Common.</p>
      <div class="sect4" lang="en">
        <div class="titlepage">
          <div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="title"><a name="id1820735"/>Combat</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
          <div class="keyword">monsterinfo</div>
        </div>
        <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersG181"/>
        <p><a href="ch66s16.html#MonstersG180">Griffons</a> prefer to pounce on their prey, either diving to the attack or leaping from above.</p>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id1820766"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersG182"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Pounce (Ex):</strong></span> If a <a href="ch66s16.html#MonstersG180">griffon</a> dives upon or charges a foe, it can make a full attack, including two rake attacks.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id1820804"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersG183"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Rake (Ex):</strong></span> Attack bonus +8 melee, damage 1d6+2.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id1820833"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersG184"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Skills:</strong></span> <a href="ch66s16.html#MonstersG180">Griffons</a> have a +4 racial bonus on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills192">Jump</a> and <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills294">Spot</a> checks.</p>
        </div>
